    <h1 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="1:1-1:7">
      <a aria-hidden="true" href="#about" class="anchor" id="user-content-about"></a>ABOUT</h1>
    <p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="2:1-2:141">Here are some important points about the project:</p>
    <ul dir="auto" data-sourcepos="3:1-8:105">
      <li data-sourcepos="3:1-3:76">the project code is available on <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/viniciusgb4/rails-calendar">github</a>;</li>
      <li data-sourcepos="3:1-3:76">the project was made in Rails 7 with Bootstrap 5 to help in the frontend;</li>
      <li data-sourcepos="4:1-4:58">the user access control was implemented with Devise gem;</li>
      <li data-sourcepos="5:1-5:90">the calendar are automatically updated with new reminders. For that, I used ActionCable;</li>
      <li data-sourcepos="6:1-6:45">the project runs inside a Docker container;</li>
      <li data-sourcepos="8:1-8:105">the interface has a dark and a light theme, that is applied accordingly with the browser configuration:</li>
    </ul>
